<item>
            <title>[LU-821] Weird quota info</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-821</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At CEA they have a weird situation where a user presumably has only 8 GBs of data, whereas the quota commands report a usage of several TBs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So we would like to know where the quota information is stored by Lustre:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;special hidden files in the file system?&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;files on the MDT (that could be accessed by mounting the MDT as ldiskfs) ?&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;files on the OSTs?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;TIA,&lt;br/&gt;
Sebastien.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
